799911165242925427.Text: Ranis asked me to convince Llarar Bereloth to join the guild. If he cannot be convinced, I must kill him. To get to Sulipund, I should leave Balmora east and pass Fort Moonmoth. Then cross the bridge to Molag Amur and follow the trail east until I reach a lake. I should see a Dunmer stronghold to the south. If I head north on the path between the hills, Sulipund will be on my left, just before the path splits.

2213415512114329032.Text: I convinced Llarar Bereloth to join the Mages Guild. I should report my success to Ranis Athrys in Balmora.

33971608031362531.Text: I reported my success to Ranis Athrys in Balmora.

18221248862756332400.Text: Mages Guild: Recruit or Kill Llarar Bereloth
